CM_ SG_ 640 WinPosnStsAtReLe "Signal sent to inform the rest of the car of the window position status for the rear driver side door. The value of the signal is either an approximated percentage of openness, of the window is moving or if the position is unkown.

";
CM_ SG_ 640 WinPosnStsAtReRi "Signal sent to inform the rest of the car of the window position status for the rear passenger side door. The value of the signal is either an approximated percentage of openness, of the window is moving or if the position is unkown.
";
